parameters: \N<Hinata Aki> No... talk to me for a bit...!
\N<Forest road> Hehe... Your hands... are trembling, huh?

\N<Forest Road's Friend A> Wow, your legs and hands are
really trembling, huh?

\N<Forest Road's Friend B> You're desperately resisting, but
you're scared, huh? Hehehe...

\N<Forest road> I've been trying to sweet-talk you all this
time, but you keep saying cold things.
\N<Forest road> How did it end up like this?

\N<Forest road> Come to think of it... that person who's
always with you... is it Taro?

\N<Forest road> It seems like that person was waiting for
you in front of the school gate, you know~

\N<Forest road> When we tried to pay a little attention to
them, they got scared and ran away.

\N<Forest road> You should become my woman instead of that
guy... Don't you understand that it would be better?

\N<Forest road> I'll treat you with lots of love, so don't
resist too much, okay?

\N<Hinata Aki>(No... I can't break free even if I resist
against three people...)

\N<Forest road's Friend A> Man... this is the first time
I've seen such huge breasts. I can't control my
excitement...

\N<Forest road's Friend B> Oh, me too... Hey sis, can you
sandwich mine with that huge one?

\N<Forest road> Hehe... don't break her so easily, okay?
She's my cute underclassman, you know?

\N<Omura> Hey, Hayamichi... What are you doing surrounding
Aki?
\N<Omura> And those two over there are outsiders, huh~

\N<Omura> What's the matter that you can't talk unless you
bring three guys into the club room?

\N<Omura> ...Well, I'll let it slide this time, but don't
you dare do something like this again.

\N<Forest road>(Jeez... making me go along with such a
crappy act...)
